staggering.%20According%20to%20one%202023%20estimate%20from%20McKinsey%2C%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20it's%20expected%20to%20add%20more%20value%20to%20the%20global%20economy%20annually%20than%20the%20entire%20GDP%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20GenAI's%20ability%20to%20almost%20instantaneously%20produce%20authentic-seeming%20content%20at%20mass%20scale%20has%20created%20the%20equally%20staggering%20potential%20to%20harm%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20ChatGPT's%20debut%20in%202022%2C%20online%20businesses%20have%20had%20to%20navigate%20a%20rapidly%20expanding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-deepfake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeepfake%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20it's%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20discern%20whether%20any%20text%2C%20call%2C%20or%20email%20is%20real%20or%20a%20scam.%20In%20the%20past%20year%20alone%2C%20GenAI-enabled%20scams%20have%20quadrupled%2C%20according%20to%20the%20scam%20reporting%20platform%20Chainabuse.%20In%20a%20Nationwide%20insurance%20survey%20of%20small%20business%20owners%20last%20fall%2C%20a%20quarter%20reported%20having%20faced%20at%20least%20one%20AI%20scam%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-copilot-licenses-million-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20%3C%2Fa%3Esays%20it%20now%20shuts%20down%20nearly%201.6%20million%20bot-based%20signup%20attempts%20every%20hour.%20Ren%C3%A9e%20DiResta%2C%20who%20researches%20online%20adversarial%20abuse%20at%20Georgetown%20University%2C%20tells%20me%20she%20calls%20the%20GenAI%20boom%20the%20%26quot%3Bindustrial%20revolution%20for%20scams%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20as%20it%20automates%20frauds%2C%20lowers%20barriers%20to%20entry%2C%20reduces%20costs%2C%20and%20increases%20access%20to%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consequences%20of%20falling%20for%20an%20AI-manipulated%20scam%20can%20be%20devastating.%20Last%20year%2C%20a%20finance%20clerk%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F05%2F16%2Ftech%2Farup-deepfake-scam-loss-hong-kong-intl-hnk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengineering%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E%20Arup%20joined%20a%20video%20call%20with%20whom%20he%20believed%20were%20his%20colleagues.%20It%20turned%20out%20that%20each%20of%20the%20attendees%20was%20a%20deepfake%20recreation%20of%20a%20real%20coworker%2C%20including%20the%20organization's%20chief%20financial%20officer.%20The%20fraudsters%20asked%20the%20clerk%20to%20approve%20overseas%20transfers%20amounting%20to%20more%20than%20%2425%20million%2C%20and%20assuming%20the%20request%20came%20through%20the%20CFO%2C%20he%20green-lit%20the%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20professionals%20in%20several%20industries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20recruitment%2C%20graphic%20design%2C%20publishing%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-doctor-shortage-med-students-primary-care-family-medicine-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20scrambling%20to%20keep%20themselves%20and%20their%20customers%20safe%20against%20AI's%20ever-evolving%20threats.%20Many%20feel%20like%20they're%20playing%20an%20endless%20game%20of%20whack-a-mole%2C%20and%20the%20moles%20are%20only%20multiplying%20and%20getting%20more%20cunning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20fraudsters%20used%20AI%20to%20build%20a%20French-language%20replica%20of%20the%20online%20Japanese%20knives%20store%20Oishya%2C%20and%20sent%20automated%20scam%20offers%20to%20the%20company's%2010%2C000-plus%20followers%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20fake%20company%20told%20customers%20of%20the%20real%20company%20they%20had%20won%20a%20free%20knife%20and%20that%20all%20they%20had%20to%20do%20was%20pay%20a%20small%20shipping%20fee%20to%20claim%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20nearly%20100%20people%20fell%20for%20it.%20Kamila%20Hankiewicz%2C%20who%20has%20run%20Oishya%20for%20nine%20years%2C%20learned%20about%20the%20scam%20only%20after%20several%20victims%20contacted%20her%20asking%20how%20long%20they%20needed%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20parcel%20to%20arrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20rude%20awakening%20for%20Hankiewicz.%20She's%20since%20ramped%20up%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-hacked-scattered-spider-cybersecurity-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20now%20runs%20campaigns%20to%20teach%20customers%20how%20to%20spot%20fake%20communications.%20Though%20many%20of%20her%20customers%20were%20upset%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-offers-scam-text-layoffs-unemployment-indeed-ftc-remote-work-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20defrauded%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hankiewicz%20helped%20them%20file%20reports%20with%20their%20financial%20institutions%20for%20refunds.%20Rattling%20as%20the%20experience%20was%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20incident%20actually%20strengthened%20our%20relationship%20with%20many%20customers%20who%20appreciated%20our%20proactive%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Duncan%2C%20the%20VP%20of%20strategy%20at%20the%20cybersecurity%20firm%20Netcraft%2C%20isn't%20surprised%20at%20the%20surge%20in%20personalized%20phishing%20attacks%20against%20small%20businesses%20like%20Oishya.%20GenAI%20tools%20now%20allow%20even%20a%20novice%20lone%20wolf%20with%20little%20technical%20know-how%20to%20clone%20a%20brand's%20image%20and%20write%20flawless%2C%20convincing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-account-scam-deepfakes-ai-voice-generator-crime-fraud-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escam%20messages%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20minutes%2C%20he%20says.%20With%20cheap%20tools%2C%20%26quot%3Battackers%20can%20more%20easily%20spoof%20employees%2C%20fool%20customers%2C%20or%20impersonate%20partners%20across%20multiple%20channels%2C%26quot%3B%20Duncan%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20mainstream%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20have%20precautions%20in%20place%20when%20you%20ask%20them%20to%20infringe%20copyright%2C%20there%20are%20now%20plenty%20of%20free%20or%20inexpensive%20online%20services%20that%20allow%20users%20to%20replicate%20a%20business's%20website%20with%20simple%20text%20prompts.%20Using%20a%20tool%20called%20Llama%20Press%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20produce%20a%20near-exact%20clone%20of%20Hankiewicz's%20store%2C%20and%20personalize%20it%20from%20a%20few%20words%20of%20instructions.%20(Kody%20Kendall%2C%20Llama%20Press's%20founder%2C%20says%20cloning%20a%20store%20like%20Oshiya's%20doesn't%20trigger%20a%20safety%20block%20because%20there%20can%20be%20legitimate%20reasons%20to%20do%20so%2C%20like%20when%20a%20business%20owner%20is%20trying%20to%20migrate%20their%20website%20to%20a%20new%20hosting%20platform.%20He%20adds%20that%20Llama%20Press%20relies%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-sonnet-ai-thought-process-decide-blackmail-fictional-executive-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20OpenAI's%20built-in%20safety%20checks%20to%20weed%20out%20bad-faith%20requests.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EText%20is%20just%20one%20front%20of%20the%20war%20businesses%20are%20fighting%20against%20malicious%20uses%20of%20AI.%20With%20the%20latest%20tools%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrdive.com%2Fnews%2Ffake-job-applicant-deepfake-70-minutes%2F745924%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20solo%20adversary%20%E2%80%94%20again%20with%20no%20technical%20expertise%20%E2%80%94%20as%20little%20as%20an%20hour%20to%20create%20a%20convincing%20fake%20job%20candidate%20to%20attend%20a%20video%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETatiana%20Becker%2C%20a%20tech%20recruiter%20based%20in%20New%20York%2C%20tells%20me%20deepfake%20job%20candidates%20have%20become%20an%20%26quot%3Bepidemic.%26quot%3B%20Over%20the%20past%20couple%20years%2C%20she%20has%20had%20to%20frequently%20reject%20scam%20applicants%20who%20use%20deepfake%20avatars%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheating-tech-interviews-soaring-managers-lost-gen-ai-chatgpt-coding-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echeat%20on%20interviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20she's%20able%20to%20discern%20some%20of%20their%20telltale%20signs%20of%20fakery%2C%20including%20a%20glitchy%20video%20quality%20and%20the%20candidate's%20refusal%20to%20switch%20up%20any%20element%20of%20their%20appearance%20during%20the%20call%2C%20such%20as%20taking%20off%20their%20headphones.%20Now%2C%20at%20the%20start%20of%20every%20interview%20she%20asks%20for%20the%20candidates'%20ID%20and%20poses%20more%20open-ended%20questions%2C%20like%20what%20they%20like%20to%20do%20in%20their%20free%20time%2C%20to%20suss%20out%20if%20they're%20a%20human.%20Ironically%2C%20she's%20made%20herself%20more%20robotic%20at%20the%20outset%20of%20interviews%20to%20sniff%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhumanoid-robots-reshape-warehouses-tech-invests-billions-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobots%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicole%20Yelland%2C%20a%20PR%20executive%2C%20says%20she%20found%20herself%20on%20the%20opposite%20end%20of%20deepfakery%20earlier%20this%20year.%20A%20scammer%20impersonating%20a%20startup%20recruiter%20approached%20her%20over%20email%20saying%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20head%20of%20comms%2C%20with%20an%20offer%20package%20that%20included%20generous%20pay%20and%20benefits.%20The%20purported%20person%20even%20shared%20with%20her%20an%20exhaustive%20slide%20deck%2C%20decorated%20with%20AI-generated%20visuals%2C%20outlining%20the%20role's%20responsibilities%20and%20benefits.%20Enticed%2C%20she%20scheduled%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20video%20meeting%2C%20however%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bhiring%20manager%26quot%3B%20refused%20to%20speak%2C%20and%20instead%20asked%20Yelland%20to%20type%20her%20responses%20to%20the%20written%20questions%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-internal-memo-using-ai-no-longer-optional-github-copilot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20Teams%3C%2Fa%3E%20chat%20section.%20Her%20alarm%20bells%20really%20went%20off%20once%20the%20interviewer%20started%20asking%20her%20to%20share%20a%20series%20of%20private%20documents%2C%20including%20her%20driver's%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYelland%20now%20runs%20a%20background%20check%20with%20tools%20like%20Spokeo%20before%20engaging%20with%20any%20stranger%20online.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20annoying%20and%20takes%20more%20time%2C%20but%20engaging%20with%20a%20spammer%20is%20more%20annoying%20and%20time-consuming%3B%20so%20this%20is%20where%20we%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskype-died-microsoft-destroyed-zoom-whatsapp-facetime-videoconferencing-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideoconferencing%20platforms%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-teams%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETeams%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Zoom%20are%20getting%20better%20at%20detecting%20AI-generated%20accounts%2C%20some%20experts%20say%20the%20detection%20itself%20risks%20creating%20an%20vicious%20cycle.%20The%20data%20these%20platforms%20collect%20on%20what's%20fake%20is%20ultimately%20used%20to%20train%20more%20sophisticated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-leaders-genai-increased-hiring-teams-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGenAI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20will%20help%20them%20get%20better%20at%20escaping%20fakery%20detectors%20and%20fuel%20%26quot%3Ban%20arms%20race%20defenders%20cannot%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jasson%20Casey%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Beyond%20Identity%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20firm%20that%20specializes%20in%20identity%20theft.%20Casey%20and%20his%20company%20believe%20the%20focus%20should%20instead%20be%20on%20authenticating%20a%20person's%20identity.%20Beyond%20Identity%20sells%20tools%20that%20can%20be%20plugged%20into%20Zoom%20that%20verify%20meeting%20participants%20through%20their%20device's%20biometrics%20and%20location%20data.%20If%20it%20detects%20a%20discrepancy%2C%20the%20tools%20label%20the%20participants'%20video%20feed%20as%20%26quot%3Bunverified.%26quot%3B%20Tram%C3%A8r%20Florian%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20professor%20at%20ETH%20Zurich%2C%20agrees%20that%20authenticating%20identity%20will%20likely%20become%20more%20essential%20to%20ensure%20that%20you're%20always%20talking%20to%20a%20legitimate%20colleague.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffake-check-job-scam-linkedin-recruiter-verification-tools-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20fake%20job%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20entrepreneurs%20now%20have%20to%20contend%20with%2C%20it's%20always%20fake%20versions%20of%20themselves.%20In%20late%202024%2C%20scammers%20ran%20ads%20on%20Facebook%20for%20a%20video%20featuring%20Jonathan%20Shaw%2C%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20Baker%20Heart%20and%20Diabetes%20Institute%20in%20Melbourne.%20Although%20the%20person%20in%20it%20looked%20and%20sounded%20exactly%20like%20Dr.%20Shaw%2C%20the%20voice%20had%20been%20deepfaked%20and%20edited%20to%20say%20that%20metformin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20first-line%20treatment%20for%20type%202%20diabetes%20%E2%80%94%20is%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20patients%20should%20instead%20switch%20to%20an%20unproven%20dietary%20supplement.%20The%20fake%20ad%20was%20accompanied%20by%20a%20fake%20written%20news%20interview%20with%20Shaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20his%20clinic's%20patients%2C%20believing%20the%20video%20was%20genuine%2C%20reached%20out%20asking%20how%20to%20get%20a%20hold%20of%20the%20supplement.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20my%20longstanding%20patients%20asked%20me%20how%20come%20I%20continued%20to%20prescribe%20metformin%20to%20him%2C%20when%20'I'%20had%20said%20on%20the%20video%20that%20it%20was%20a%20poor%20drug%2C%26quot%3B%20Shaw%20tells%20me.%20Eventually%20he%20was%20able%20to%20get%20Facebook%20to%20take%20down%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20equally%20vexing%20and%20annoying%20issue%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-facebook-ban-ai-slop-images-shrimp-jesus-why-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20slop%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20inundation%20of%20low-quality%2C%20mass-produced%20images%20and%20text%20that%20is%20flooding%20the%20internet%20and%20making%20it%20ever-more%20difficult%20for%20the%20average%20person%20to%20tell%20what's%20real%20or%20fake.%20In%20her%20research%2C%20DiResta%20found%20instances%20where%20social%20platforms'%20recommendation%20engines%20have%20promoted%20malicious%20slop%20%E2%80%94%20where%20scammers%20would%20put%20up%20images%20of%20items%20like%20nonexistent%20rental%20properties%2C%20appliances%2C%20and%20more%20that%20users%20were%20frequently%20falling%20for%20it%20and%20giving%20away%20their%20payment%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Pinterest%2C%20AI-generated%20%26quot%3Binspo%26quot%3B%20posts%20have%20plagued%20people's%20mood%20boards%20%E2%80%94%20so%20much%20so%20that%20Philadelphia-based%20Cake%20Life%20Shop%20now%20often%20receives%20orders%20from%20customers%20asking%20them%20to%20recreate%20what%20are%20actually%20AI-generated%20cakes.%20In%20one%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20cake%20resembles%20a%20moss-filled%20rainforest%2C%20and%20features%20a%20functional%20waterfall.%20Thankfully%20for%20cofounder%20Nima%20Etemadi%2C%20most%20customers%20are%20%26quot%3Breceptive%20to%20hearing%20about%20what%20is%20possible%20with%20real%20cake%20after%20we%20burst%20their%20AI%20bubble%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20AI-generated%20books%20have%20swarmed%20Amazon%20and%20are%20now%20hurting%20publisher%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPauline%20Frommer%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-sad-decline-lonely-planet-america-coolest-travel-guide-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20guide%20publisher%3C%2Fa%3E%20Frommer%20Media%2C%20says%20that%20AI-generated%20guidebooks%20have%20managed%20to%20reach%20the%20top%20of%20lists%20with%20the%20help%20of%20fake%20reviews.%20An%20AI%20publisher%20buys%20a%20few%20Prime%20memberships%2C%20sets%20the%20guidebook's%20ebook%20price%20to%20zero%2C%20and%20then%20leaves%20seemingly%20%26quot%3Bverified%20reviews%26quot%3B%20by%20downloading%20its%20copies%20for%20free.%20These%20practices%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bwill%20make%20it%20virtually%20impossible%20for%20a%20new%2C%20legitimate%20brand%20of%20guidebook%20to%20enter%20the%20business%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%20Ian%20Lamont%20says%20he%20received%20an%20AI-generated%20guidebook%20as%20a%20gift%20last%20year%3A%20a%20text-only%20guide%20to%20Taiwan%2C%20with%20no%20pictures%20or%20maps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20FTC%20now%20considers%20it%20illegal%20to%20publish%20fake%2C%20AI-generated%20product%20reviews%2C%20official%20policies%20haven't%20yet%20caught%20up%20with%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedia-ai-artificial-intelligence-youtube-tiktok-algorithm-ads-creative-hollywood-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20AI-generated%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20itself.%20Platforms%20like%20Pinterest%20and%20Google%20have%20started%20to%20watermark%20and%20label%20AI-generated%20posts%2C%20but%20since%20it's%20not%20error-free%20yet%2C%20some%20worry%20these%20measures%20may%20do%20more%20harm%20than%20good.%20DiResta%20fears%20that%20a%20potential%20unintended%20consequence%20of%20ubiquitous%20AI%20labels%20would%20be%20people%20experiencing%20%26quot%3Blabel%20fatigue%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20they%20blindly%20assume%20that%20unlabeled%20content%20is%20therefore%20always%20%26quot%3Breal.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20potentially%20dangerous%20assumption%20if%20a%20sophisticated%20manipulator%2C%20like%20a%20state%20actor's%20intelligence%20service%2C%20manages%20to%20get%20disinformation%20content%20past%20a%20labeler%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20small%20business%20owners%20should%20stay%20vigilant%2C%20says%20Robin%20Pugh%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Intelligence%20for%20Good%2C%20a%20non-profit%20that%20helps%20victims%20of%20internet-enabled%20crimes.%20They%20should%20always%20validate%20they're%20dealing%20with%20an%20actual%20human%20and%20that%20the%20money%20they're%20sending%20is%20actually%20going%20where%20they%20intend%20it%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEtemadi%20of%20Cake%20Life%20Shop%20recognizes%20that%20for%20as%20much%20as%20GenAI%20can%20help%20his%20business%20become%20more%20efficient%2C%20scam%20artists%20will%20ultimately%20use%20the%20same%20tools%20to%20become%20just%20as%20efficient.%20%26quot%3BDoing%20business%20online%20gets%20more%20necessary%20and%20high%20risk%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20just%20part%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fshubham-agarwal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EShubham%20Agarwal%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20freelance%20technology%20journalist%20from%20Ahmedabad%2C%20India%2C%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Wired%2C%20The%20Verge%2C%20Fast%20Company%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-small-business-owners-swamped-by-scammers-generative-ai-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751357341000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862f43a3d5881a5