s%20500%20open%20robotics%20roles%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20isn't%20all%20doom%20and%20gloom%20for%20jobs%2C%20said%20Amazon's%20Andy%20Jassy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20published%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandy-jassy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%20CEO%20%3C%2Fa%3Edeemed%20AI%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20transformative%20technology%20in%20our%20lifetime.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20it%20would%20change%20things%20not%20only%20for%20Amazon%20customers%20but%20also%20for%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20said%20that%20AI%20technologies%20would%20create%20jobs%20in%20at%20least%20two%20areas%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20every%20technical%20transformation%2C%20there%20will%20be%20fewer%20people%20doing%20some%20of%20the%20jobs%20that%20the%20technology%20actually%20starts%20to%20automate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAre%20there%20going%20to%20be%20other%20jobs%3F%20We're%20going%20to%20hire%20more%20people%20in%20AI%20and%20more%20people%20in%20robotics%2C%20and%20there%20are%20going%20to%20be%20other%20jobs%20that%20the%20technology%20wants%20you%20to%20go%20higher%20that%20we'll%20hire%20over%20time%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20said%20that%20AI%20agents%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-deploy-cursor-employee-interest-spikes-ai-coding-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edo%20tasks%20like%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20research%2C%20analytics%2C%20and%20spreadsheet%20work%2C%20would%20also%20change%20the%20nature%20of%20every%20employee's%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20won't%20have%20to%20do%20as%20much%20rote%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20person%20gets%20to%20start%20every%20task%20at%20a%20more%20advanced%20starting%20spot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20LinkedIn%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAmazon%20has%20added%20