every%20hour%20--%20more%20than%208%2C71%2C000%20deaths%20annually%20between%202014%20and%202023%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20by%20the%20World%20Health%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2F1-in-6-people-affected-by-loneliness-worldwide-who-8806004%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft%20says%20its%20new%20health%20AI%20beat%20doctors%20in%20accurate%20diagnoses%20by%20a%20mile%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microsoft%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686363273d5881a51c1c6958%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0Microsoft%20said%20its%20medical%20AI%20diagnosed%20cases%20four%20times%20as%20accurately%20as%20human%20doctors.%3Cp%3EMatthias%20Balk%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMicrosoft%20said%20its%20medical%20AI%20diagnosed%20cases%20four%20times%20as%20accurately%20as%20human%20doctors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20system%20also%20solved%20cases%20%26quot%3Bmore%20cost-effectively%26quot%3B%20than%20its%20human%20counterparts%2C%20Microsoft%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20study%20comes%20as%20AI's%20growing%20role%20in%20healthcare%20raises%20questions%20about%20its%20place%20in%20medicine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20said%20its%20medical%20AI%20system%20diagnosed%20cases%20more%20accurately%20than%20human%20doctors%20by%20a%20wide%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20blog%20post%20published%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20said%20its%20AI%20system%2C%20the%20Microsoft%20AI%20Diagnostic%20Orchestrator%2C%20diagnosed%20cases%20four%20times%20as%20accurately%20as%20a%20group%20of%20experienced%20physicians%20in%20a%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft's%20study%20comes%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbots-tech-doctors-medicine-healthcare-system-empathy-quality-email-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%20rapidly%20make%20their%20way%20into%20hospitals%20and%20clinics%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20raising%20questions%20about%20how%20much%20of%20medicine%20can%20or%20should%20be%20automated%20and%20what%20role%20doctors%20will%20play%20as%20diagnostic%20AI%20systems%20get%20more%20capable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experiment%20involved%20304%20case%20studies%20sourced%20from%20the%20New%20England%20Journal%20of%20Medicine.%20Both%20the%20AI%20and%20physicians%20had%20to%20solve%20these%20cases%20step%20by%20step%2C%20just%20like%20they%20would%20in%20a%20real%20clinic%3A%20ordering%20tests%2C%20asking%20questions%2C%20and%20narrowing%20down%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20system%20was%20paired%20with%20large%20language%20models%20from%20tech%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20Meta%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20Google.%20When%20coupled%20with%20OpenAI's%20o3%2C%20the%20AI%20diagnostic%20system%20correctly%20solved%2085.5%25%20of%20the%20cases%2C%20Microsoft%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%2021%20practicing%20physicians%20from%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20each%20with%20five%20to%2020%20years%20of%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20averaged%2020%25%20accuracy%20across%20the%20completed%20cases%2C%20the%20company%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eadded.%20In%20the%20study%2C%20the%20doctors%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20resources%20they%20might%20typically%20tap%20for%20diagnostics%2C%20including%20coworkers%2C%20books%2C%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20system%20also%20solved%20cases%20%26quot%3Bmore%20cost-effectively%26quot%3B%20than%20its%20human%20counterparts%2C%20Microsoft%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20findings%20also%20suggest%20that%20AI%20reduce%20unnecessary%20healthcare%20costs.%20US%20health%20spending%20is%20nearing%2020%25%20of%20US%20GDP%2C%20with%20up%20to%2025%25%20of%20that%20estimated%20to%20be%20wasted%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20taking%20a%20big%20step%20towards%20medical%20superintelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmustafa-suleyman-microsoft-ai-first-business-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMustafa%20Suleyman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Microsoft's%20AI%20division%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20cases%20used%20in%20the%20study%20are%20%26quot%3Bsome%20of%20the%20toughest%20and%20most%20diagnostically%20complex%26quot%3B%20a%20physician%20can%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuleyman%20previously%20led%20AI%20efforts%20at%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7ef3242-7ec9-44b8-a77d-f4e153f3ee27%5C%22%3EWill%20AI%20replace%20doctors%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20said%20in%20the%20blog%20post%20that%20AI%20%26quot%3Brepresents%20a%20complement%20to%20doctors%20and%20other%20health%20professionals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20technology%20is%20advancing%20rapidly%2C%20their%20clinical%20roles%20are%20much%20broader%20than%20simply%20making%20a%20diagnosis.%20They%20need%20to%20navigate%20ambiguity%20and%20build%20trust%20with%20patients%20and%20their%20families%20in%20a%20way%20that%20AI%20isn't%20set%20up%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClinical%20roles%20will%2C%20we%20believe%2C%20evolve%20with%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20leaders%20like%20Microsoft%20cofounder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-ai-job-shortages-doctors-teachers-work-free-time-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates%20have%20said%20that%20AI%20could%20help%20solve%20the%20long-standing%20shortage%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20will%20come%20in%20and%20provide%20medical%20IQ%2C%20and%20there%20won't%20be%20a%20shortage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BPeople%20by%20WTF%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20doctors%20have%20told%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBI%20that%20AI%20can't%20and%20shouldn't%20replace%20clinicians%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-changing-home-care-doctors-clinicians-speedoc-singapore-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20can't%20replicate%20physicians'%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epresence%2C%20empathy%2C%20and%20nuanced%20judgment%20in%20uncertain%20or%20complex%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Shravan%20Verma%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20Singapore-based%20health%20tech%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatbots%20and%20AI%20tools%20can%20handle%20the%20first%20mile%20of%20care%2C%20but%20they%20must%20escalate%20to%20qualified%20professionals%20when%20needed%2C%20he%20told%20BI%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20AI%20in%20healthcare%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acmlee%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecmlee%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajsmith%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-diagnosed-accurate-doctors-medicine-study-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751352348000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68636386f748d8c055f4b0f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-diagnosed-accurate-doctors-medicine-study-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3