Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn5kk1w00xyo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%20100%20US%20companies%20hiring%20remote%20workers%20ended%20up%20funding%20Kim%20Jong%20Un's%20weapons%20programs%2C%20DOJ%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223665%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20this%20photo%20provided%20by%20the%20North%20Korean%20government%2C%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%2C%20center%2C%20supervises%20a%20drill%20of%20long-range%20artillery%20and%20missile%20systems%20at%20North%20Korea's%20eastern%20coast%20in%20May.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68635ceb3d5881a51c1c691e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222405%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20its%20latest%20crackdown%20against%20North%20Korea's%20attempts%20to%20get%20its%20workers%20hired%20in%20American%20firms%2C%20the%20DOJ%20said%20Pyongyang%20used%20%26quot%3Blaptop%20farms%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20company%20computers%20plugged%20into%20hard%20drives%20that%20Kim%20Jong%20Un's%20workers%20could%20access.%3Cp%3EKorean%20Central%20News%20Agency%2FKorea%20News%20Service%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20said%20over%20100%20US%20firms%20were%20unknowingly%20paying%20salaries%20to%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20said%20the%20scheme%20involved%20%26quot%3Blaptop%20farms%26quot%3B%20of%20work%20computers%20for%20US%20firms%20plugged%20into%20hard%20drives.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENorth%20Korean%20IT%20workers%20could%20then%20access%20the%20computers%20and%20earn%20salaries%20from%20the%20US%20firms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20had%20seized%20hundreds%20of%20computers%20and%20accused%2013%20people%20of%20tricking%20US%20companies%20into%20paying%20salaries%20to%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20new%20indictment%20filed%20in%20Massachusetts%20federal%20court%2C%20prosecutors