%2C%20my%20father%20never%20once%20insisted%20that%20I%20take%20on%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20farming%20or%20tending%20to%20the%20buffalo.%20Even%20my%20mother%20never%20forced%20me%20to%20go%20to%20the%20flour%20mill%20to%20grind%20grains.%20Instead%2C%20my%20parents%20encouraged%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20education.%20They%20placed%20all%20their%20faith%20in%20my%20education%2C%20and%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20betray%20that%20trust.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Rahman%20was%20just%20a%20child%20when%20he%20learnt%20one%20of%20life%E2%80%99s%20harshest%20lessons.%20Once%2C%20he%20accompanied%20his%20ailing%20mother%20and%20younger%20brother%20to%20a%20hospital.%20They%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20pay%20for%20two%20separate%20consultations%2C%20which%20led%20to%20humiliation%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20compounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20about%20five%20or%20six%20years%20old%20when%20my%20mother%20took%20me%20and%20my%20younger%20brother%20to%20a%20hospital.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20money%2C%20so%20she%20asked%20the%20compounder%20if%20both%20of%20us%20could%20be%20treated%20under%20the%20same%20prescription%20to%20save%20money.%20He%20reacted%20harshly%2C%20scolding%20us%20for%20being%20poor.%20I%20was%20too%20young%20to%20understand%20everything%2C%20but%20I%20remember%20the%20shame%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20doctor%2C%20whom%20I%20revered%20and%20still%20consider%20my%20role%20model%2C%20was%20compassionate%20and%20did%20not%20treat%20us%20poorly.%20This%20experience%20stayed%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indignity%20of%20being%20scolded%20for%20poverty%20became%20a%20turning