'%26quot%3B%20Fyall%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20all%20comes%20back%20to%20the%20bigger%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECacciari%20said%20the%20goal%20is%20not%20to%20do%20away%20with%20all%20tourism%2C%20especially%20since%20many%20Venetians%20rely%20on%20the%20income%20from%20foreign%20travelers%2C%20but%20that%20a%20better%20balance%20needed%20to%20be%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20like%20the%20slogan%20'Tourists%20go%20home%2C'%20for%20example.%20No%2C%20tourists%20are%20welcome%20as%20long%20as%20there%20is%20a%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20Cacciari%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20the%20measure%20is%20broken%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20tourist's%20fault.%20It's%20the%20one%20who%20runs%20the%20city's%20fault.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECity%20officials%20had%20welcomed%20the%20wedding.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20happy%20and%20honoured%20to%20welcome%20Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20his%20consort%20Lauren%20S%C3%A1nchez%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayor%20Luigi%20Brugnaro%20said%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20dissuade%20mass%20travel%2C%20the%20city%20has%20implemented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvenice-tourism-group-cap-overtourism-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etourist%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20charging%20day-trip%20visitors%20about%20%245%20to%20enter%20the%20city%20center%20on%20certain%20days%2C%20and%20limited%20tour%20group%20numbers%20to%20a%20maximum%20of%2025%2C%20as%20well%20as%20restricted%20the%20use%20of%20loudspeakers.%20They've%20also%20instituted%20restrictions%20on%20cruise%20ships.%20But%20despite%20those%20efforts%2C%20overtourism%20concerns%20have%20remained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFyall%20said%20the%20persistent%20nature%20of%20the%20protests%20shows%20that%20the%20city%20has%20not%20yet%20fully%20addressed%20its%20residents'%20concerns.%20Until%20it%20does%2C%20we%20can%20expect%20to%20see%20more%20protests%20like%20the%20ones%20targeted%20at%20Bezos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20origi