charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686300a285e81483682d157a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProtesters%20pose%20outside%20Google%20DeepMind's%20office.%3Cp%3EHugh%20Langley%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPauseAI%20argues%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-shoppers-google-amazon-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20broke%20a%20promise%20it%20made%20during%20the%202024%20AI%20Safety%20Summit%20in%20Seoul%2C%20Korea%2C%20when%20the%20company%20agreed%20to%20consider%20external%20evaluations%20of%20its%20models%20and%20publish%20details%20about%20how%20external%20parties%2C%20including%20governments%2C%20were%20involved%20in%20assessing%20the%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Google%20launched%20Gemini%202.5%20Pro%2C%20its%20latest%20frontier%20model%2C%20in%20April%2C%20it%20did%20neither%20of%20those%20things.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20was%20because%20the%20model%20was%20still%20%26quot%3Bexperimental.%26quot%3B%20A%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20it%20released%20a%20%26quot%3Bmodel%20card%26quot%3B%20with%20some%20safety%20details%2C%20which%20some%20experts%20criticized%20for%20being%20too%20thin%20on%20details%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fmodel-cards%2Fdocuments%2Fgemini-2.5-pro-preview.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETechCrunch%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20reported.%20While%20the%20safety%20report%20made%20reference%20to%20third-party%20testers%2C%20it%20did%20not%20specify%20who%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20PauseAI%2C%20this%20isn't%20good%20enough.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20organization%20said%2C%20it's%20about%20not%20letting%20any%20lapse%20slip%20by%20and%20allowing%20Google%20to%20set%20a%20precedent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20let%20Google%20get%20away%20with%20breaking%20their%20word%2C%20it%20sends%20a%20signal%20to%20all%20other%20labs%20that%20safety%20promises%20aren't%20important%20and%20commitments%20to%20the%20public%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20kept%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PauseAI%20organizing%20director%20Ella%20Hughes%2C%20addressing%20the%20crowd%2C%20which%20had%20gradually%20swelled%20to%20around%2060%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20AI%20companies%20are%20less%20regulated%20than%20sandwich%20shops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DeepMind%20protestors%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862ec5d3d5881a51c1c6459%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProtesters%20demonstrate%20at%20London's%20King's%20Cross.%3Cp%3EHugh%20Langley%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20to%20worry%20about%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI.%20Economic%20disruption.%20Job%20displacement.%20Misinformation.%20Deepfakes.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-only-chance-of-annihilation-with-ai-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20annihilation%20of%20humanity%20as%20we%20know%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFocusing%20on%20the%20specific%20issue%20of%20the%20Google%20safety%20report%20is%20a%20way%20for%20PauseAI%20to%20push%20for%20a%20specific%20and%20attainable%20near-term%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2030%20minutes%20into%20the%20protest%2C%20several%20intrigued%20passers-by%20had%20joined%20the%20cause.%20After%20a%20rousing%20speech%20from%20Hughes%2C%20the%20group%20proceeded%20to%20Google%20DeepMind's%20offices%2C%20where%20the%20fake%20courtroom%20production%20played%20out.%20Some%20Google%20employees%20leaving%20for%20the%20day%20looked%20bemused%20as%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3BStop%20the%20race%2C%20it's%20unsafe%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTest%2C%20don't%20guess%26quot%3B%20rang%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20regulation%20on%20an%20international%20level%20is%20in%20a%20very%20bad%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20PauseAI%20founder%20Joep%20Meindertsma%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20pointing%20to%20how%20US%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.presidency.ucsb.edu%2Fdocuments%2Fremarks-the-vice-president-the-artificial-intelligence-action-summit-paris-france%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%20against%20over-regulating%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20AI%20Action%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protestors%20at%20Google%20DeepMind%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862ead53d5881a51c1c6406%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20fake%20courtroom%20trial%20takes%20place%20outside%20Google%20DeepMind's%20office.%3Cp%3EHugh%20Langley%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMonday%20was%20the%20first%20time%20PauseAI%20had%20gathered%20over%20this%20specific%20issue%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20clear%20what%20comes%20next.%20The%20group%20is%20engaging%20with%20members%20of%20UK%20parliament%20who%20will%20run%20these%20concerns%20up%20the%20flagpole%2C%20but%20Meindertsma%20is%20reticent%20to%20say%20much%20about%20how%20Google%20is%20engaging%20with%20the%20group%20and%20their%20demands%20(a%20Google%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20for%20this%20story).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeindertsma%20hopes%20support%20will%20grow%20and%20references%20polls%20that%20suggest%20the%20public%20at%20large%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F7213096%2Fuk-public-ai-law-poll%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcerned%20that%20AI%20is%20moving%20too%20fast%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20group%20on%20Monday%20was%20made%20up%20of%20people%20from%20different%20backgrounds%2C%20including%20some%20who%20work%20in%20tech.%20Meindertsma%20himself%20runs%20a%20software%20development%20company%20and%20regularly%20uses%20AI%20tools%20from%20Google%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20tools%20are%20incredibly%20impressive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20the%20thing%20that%20worries%20me%20so%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20something%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahlangley%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehlangley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20628-228-1836.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotesters-accuse-google-deepmind-breaking-promises-ai-safety-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751324041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862ddf485e81483682d10b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotesters-accuse-google-deepmind-breaking-promises-ai-safety-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Demonstrators%20gathered%20outside%20Google%20DeepMind's%20London%20office%20on%20Monday%20to%20accuse%20the%20company%20of%20reneging%20on%20a%20key%20AI%20promise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hlangley%40businessinsider.com%20(Hugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotesters-accuse-google-deepmind-breaking-promises-ai-safety-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20child%20fell%20