E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20seven%20years%2C%20I%20have%20been%20prone%20to%20acidity%2C%20and%20that%20ensured%20that%20I%20ate%20healthy%20and%20had%20most%20of%20my%20meals%20at%20home.%20I%20tried%20not%20to%20miss%20my%20meals%20or%20change%20the%20times%20of%20the%20meals%20too%20much%20to%20ensure%20that%20I%20stayed%20fine.%20I%20did%20consult%20a%20doctor%2Cr%20and%20it%20was%20diagnosed%20to%20be%20GERD%2C%20a%20gastric-related%20issue%2C%20wherein%20the%20stomach%20produces%20more%20acid%20than%20needed.%20With%20medications%2C%20the%20symptoms%20would%20decrease%2C%20but%20it%20was%20something%20that%20kept%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20after%20my%20heart%20attack%2C%20doctors%20mentioned%20that%20I%20was%20perhaps%20confusing%20the%20angina%20pain%20to%20be%20acidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMy%20biggest%20takeaway%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20entire%20experience%20was%20a%20harsh%20reminder%20of%20how%20easily%20we%20take%20our%20bodies%20for%20granted.%20We%20grow%20up%20believing%20that%20serious%20health%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20heart%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20are%20something%20that%20happen%20only%20after%2040%20or%2045.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20mindful%20about%20my%20fitness%2C%20careful%20about%20what%20I%20ate%2C%20and%20did%20everything%20I%20thought%20was%20%E2%80%9Cright.%E2%80%9D%20And%20yet%2C%20I%20had%20a%20heart%20attack%20at%2033.%20It%20shattered%20the%20illusion%20that%20age%20or%20lifestyle%20alone%20can%20shield%20us%20from%20what%E2%80%99s%20brewing%20beneath%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Six%20months%20after%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20heart%20attack.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1751272717-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458077%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESix%20months%20after%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20hardest%20lessons%20I%E2%80%99ve%20learnt%20%E2%80%94%20and%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20hard%20way%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20we%20often%20have%20no%20idea%20what%E2%80%99s%20really%20happening%20inside%20our%20bodies.%20A%20heart%20attack%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20age.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20result%20of%20a%20complex%20mix%20of%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20lifestyle%2C%20stress%2C%20genetics%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20which%20we%20tend%20to%20overlook%20until%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20we%E2%80%99re%20all%20sitting%20on%20a%20silent%20time-bomb.%20Everything%20seems%20fine%E2%80%A6%20until%20one%20day%2C%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t.%20The%20best%20way%20to%20protect%20yourself%20is%20to%20stay%20ahead%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20through%20regular%20health%20check-ups%2C%20listening%20to%20your%20body%2C%20and%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20your%20health%20parameters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20narrated%20by%20Ram%20to%20Vidya%20Raja%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDoctor%20speaks%3C%2