20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F410508%2Fhow-to-start-vermicompost-business-profitable-farmers-share-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeds%20for%20vermicompost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20each%20yielding%20more%20than%20two%20tonnes%20of%20compost.%20His%20monthly%20production%20stands%20at%20500%20tonnes%2C%20selling%20the%20vermicompost%20at%20%E2%82%B94.50%20per%20kilogram.%20With%20this%2C%20the%20business%20generates%20%E2%82%B92.5%20crore%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReminiscing%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20a%20high-profile%20corporate%20career%20to%20become%20an%20agri-entrepreneur%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20moment%20I%20chose%20farming%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20would%20not%20receive%20support%20from%20anyone.%20Everyone%20questioned%20my%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20stability%20of%20corporate%20life%2C%20but%20I%20saw%20potential%20in%20what%20others%20saw%20as%20waste.%20Despite%20hardships%2C%20I%20chose%20never%20to%20regret%20my%20decision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20understand%20and%20appreciate%20the%20challenges%20and%20rewards%20of%20entrepreneurship.%20When%20you%E2%80%99re%20doing%20your%20own%20business%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20always%20motivated.%20You%20work%2024%2F7%2C%20but%20it%20never%20feels%20like%20a%20burden.%20I%20feel%20liberated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Raj%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751194560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fvermicompost-feature-1-1751000800.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D456838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20losing%20his%20savings%20in%20the%20dairy%20business%2C%20Raj%20Singh%20pivoted%20to%20vermicomposting.%20Using%20innovative%20methods%20like%20banana%20leaves%20for%20mulching%2C%20he%20transformed%20his%20venture%20into%20a%20%E2%82%B92.5%20